    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The part of a column between the bottom of the capital and the top of the shaft, or the molding or moldings located here.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
